title: Bitcoin’s Failure to Surpass Key Resistance Level Signals Potential Downturn, Warns Top Trader
description: A prominent cryptocurrency trader has warned that the price of the flagship cryptocurrency Bitcoin ($BTC) has struggled to surpass a significant resistance level for an extended period, which to him could mean BTC could soon face significant downside.
